  ('82', '10', '2', 'hello', '2026-05-13 19:22:01', NULL),
  ('83', '10', '2', 'meow', '2026-05-13 19:28:30', '82'),
  ('84', '11', '2', 'Test', '2026-05-13 20:03:41', NULL),
  ('85', '11', '2', 'Test', '2026-05-13 20:03:49', '84'),
  ('86', '11', '2', 'Test', '2026-05-13 20:03:57', '85'),
  ('87', '12', '2', 'Well, the site is in beta, so there will be bugs. LOL  What an interesting way to report a bug. ?  If you''re not in the discord group already, there is a channel in there where you can report bugs and feedback for us to fix!  https://www.discord.gg/animecom  Feel free to DM me as well if you ever find anything!', '2026-05-15 13:43:41', NULL),
  ('88', '12', '2', 'Hahaha, sorry about that, I have a bit of a funny personality. I''m actually in your Discord server, but I usually report bugs or vulnerabilities I find in applications or webapps to the developers either through this kind of joke or via email. I actually thought it would be fun for a place like this.', '2026-05-15 13:43:58', '87'),
  ('89', '12', '2', 'clever', '2026-05-15 13:44:14', '88'),
  ('90', '12', '2', '.', '2026-05-15 13:44:23', '89'),
  ('91', '12', '2', 'LMAO, I don''t mind it, I just worry that you might report something I might not see. Posting in the Discord sends me an alert so I don''t miss it (same with DM here).   Maybe you can DM me after you do your funny thing to make sure I see it. ?', '2026-05-15 13:44:42', '88'),
  ('92', '12', '2', 'Alright sir! ? Next time i''ll do it haha.', '2026-05-15 13:45:00', '91'),
  ('93', '12', '2', 'rose i told you to add a reply option in message 10 days ago, but you didn''t even reply :'')', '2026-05-15 13:45:17', '91'),
  ('94', '12', '2', 'I think they''re working pretty hard. I''m sure they''re busy polishing more specific algorithms alongside the visual and simple modules. I think they''ve seen it, just give them some time. anime.com is a nice platform.', '2026-05-15 13:45:39', '93'),
  ('95', '12', '2', 'yupp! i know its a nice platform and the community is also so good in here!!', '2026-05-15 13:45:52', '94'),
  ('96', '12', '2', 'I Agree..', '2026-05-15 13:46:05', '95'),
  ('97', '12', '2', 'I saw it and I''m not an engineer, I can''t just "add a reply option" LOL -- We have a priority list of things we''re working through. Not EVERYTHING you suggest will get implemented immediately. Some of it is rolled down the line. ?  Plus, I think the reason I didn''t reply was because by the time I got around to all that, your Discord account was hacked so there was no point in replying to a scammer. ?  (Did you get that under control, btw?)', '2026-05-15 13:46:31', '93'),
  ('98', '12', '2', 'ah i see! yeah i got it back, i did everything i can but still they literally hacked me 3 times in a row ?', '2026-05-15 13:47:01', '97'),
  ('99', '12', '2', 'RIP ?', '2026-05-15 13:47:19', '98'),
  ('100', '12', '2', 'Whoops just a suggestion, using a password manager and creating a secure, strong password is a good solution, but if you''ve been hacked 3 times, I think the problem might be with your pc/mobile or your emails :)', '2026-05-15 13:47:34', '98');
