  ('2', '710b0a31-a0ff-74ed-b5a1-da116caec260', '2', '1', 'Hahaha, sorry about that, I have a bit of a funny personality. I''m actually in your Discord server, but I usually report bugs or vulnerabilities I find in applications or webapps to the developers either through this kind of joke or via email. I actually thought it would be fun for a place like this.', '2026-05-14 22:13:32');



If you are using Anivault for watching anime then you may have seen a ''max resources used" error while browsing. And also the site is slowing down. So you may have witness long reload time. Its happening because the max amount of ram/cpu is being used in my free hosting in this days.

For almost a year, Anivault has been running completely ad-free. Since the site had a relatively small user base, free hosting was enough to handle the traffic. However, after being added to TBCPL, a large number of new users started visiting the site, and the current free hosting can no longer keep up with the growth.

At this point, I have two possible options:

1. Display ads on the website to help cover hosting costs.
2. Accept donations and use the funds to purchase a paid hosting plan.

To help decide the future of Anivault, I''m running a simple survey. Please select the option you prefer in the voting section below.

This is only a vote—you will not see any ads right now, and you are not being asked to donate at this time.

Also, I recently opened a Discord server. Feel free to join if you''d like to stay updated, share feedback, or contact me directly.

Thank you for supporting Anivault! ❤️', '2026-06-29 14:31:11'),
